---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<Base title="Thanks — RECN">
  <Header />
  <main class="container" style="padding-top: 80px; padding-bottom: 80px; text-align: center;">
    <div class="accent-bar" style="width: 32px; margin: 0 auto var(--sp-md);"></div>
    <h1 style="font-size: 1.5rem; letter-spacing: 3px; margin-bottom: var(--sp-lg); text-transform: uppercase; font-family: var(--font-mono);">Thank you</h1>
    <div style="max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <p style="margin-bottom: var(--sp-md); font-size: 0.9375rem; line-height: 1.8;">
        I really appreciate you signing up. This means a lot.
      </p>
      <p style="margin-bottom: var(--sp-md); font-size: 0.9375rem; line-height: 1.8;">
        RECN started because I couldn't find a recording app that treated my audio with the respect it deserved. Everything wanted to upload to a cloud I didn't ask for, or locked recordings behind formats I couldn't use, or just wasn't reliable enough for the moments that matter — the 3am idea, the one-take magic in a rehearsal room.
      </p>
      <p style="margin-bottom: var(--sp-md); font-size: 0.9375rem; line-height: 1.8;">
        So I'm building what I wish existed. A simple, reliable tool that captures your audio, keeps it on your device, and gets out of the way. Transcription that runs locally. Multi-track that works on a phone. No accounts, no cloud, no subscriptions.
      </p>
      <p style="margin-bottom: var(--sp-md); font-size: 0.9375rem; line-height: 1.8;">
        You're early to this. Things will move fast, designs will change, and some things might break along the way. But the core promise won't: your recordings are sacred, and they'll always stay yours.
      </p>
      <p style="margin-bottom: var(--sp-xl); font-size: 0.9375rem; line-height: 1.8;">
        I'll keep you posted as things take shape. Thanks for believing in this before it's finished.
      </p>
      <p style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-tertiary); letter-spacing: 1px;">
        — Shubham
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Base>
